    "## What is Linear Regression?\n",
    "\n",
    "Linear Regression is a statisticial model, which is based on the assumption of a *linear* relationship between one or more variables.\n",
    "\n",
    "The linear regression model is given by:\n",
    "\n",
    "$y_i = \\beta_{0} + \\beta_{1}x_i + \\epsilon_i$\n",
    "\n",
    "The parameters $\\beta_{0}$ and $\\beta_{1}$ can be estimated using the method of ordinary least squares. "
   ]
